{"tid":194962,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"hkbn又有新plan","createTime":"2017-04-10T10:31:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T05:01:37.000Z","uid":21427,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cda827fdd21002a185486f8c71054d0eb74d19f6","tid":194962,"uid":21427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:31:34.000Z","msg":"追打 SUN Mobile! HKBN 香港寬頻 x數碼通網絡 21Mbps 計劃新低價！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人話，原來週未中國移動香港係深夜又死網，三個月三次，又的確幾得人驚，怪不得 MVNO 台 HKBN 要變陣，由原本用 CMHK 網絡嘅 21Mbps／5GB plan 搶低價市場，改回口碑比較好嘅數碼通網絡！今次搶打 SUN Mobile! 你點揀？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHKBN 香港寬頻即日 10／4 推出的 4G LTE 網絡（最高速度 21Mbps）服務（網絡夥伴：數碼通），攜號轉台至香港寬頻可享每月 5GB 數據，新 Number 為 3GB 數據用量。上述組合附設myTV SUPER 流動應用程式（基本版）；用家也可同時選擇以超值月費 $38，將家居電話轉至香港寬頻固網。呢個 Plan，跟其他 HKBN 21Mbps &nbsp;計劃一様，用爆數據後，都有無限上網，但速度變返地獄 128kbps。呢個組合，月費為 $78，當然要付行政費每月 $18，已包 HKBN &nbsp;/ Y5Zone WiFi。呢個 Plan，跟 SUN Mobile 一様，Sun Mobile 無 MyTV Super 送，亦一定要交出個人資料比 HKT 嘅 The Club。你會點揀？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0UA0828.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0UA0828.jpg&h=44aaa6dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/3149/207968/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F3149%2F207968%2F&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYqzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=ecfa6a50\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/3149/207968/</a>"},{"pid":"ef4e73d87b701015ab414a3f60188b7e149d18b6","tid":194962,"uid":22270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T11:28:04.000Z","msg":"咁電訊數碼好似快d"},{"pid":"8c98df33638e1c5cd676cdf28340354c25f5b85e","tid":194962,"uid":84951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T11:30:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a57806083c4b0e83691b545482057700c46b282","tid":194962,"uid":97985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T12:31:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55c56f1df4ab045e520e71ed1308e6